name: Synthesis of Life and Death
description:
This image is one of the early images that I generated to start a story idea. I was thinking of the idea of being in Lambo in a material world and started sketching. After a couple of images, I used CLIP guided Diffusion [by @rivershavewings] algorithm to process the drawings with various prompts. 

This image turned out so strong and effective, it turned out as a genesis idea for my Graveyard Stories [which is currently being developed] and also turned into one of my favourites. 

I couldn't fit it into my ongoing collections and kept it a secret in my metaphorical letter drawer. But with my introduction to HEN being so welcoming with the Grotesque-o-Lanterns, I decided to go with HEN to mint this special piece.

Enjoy.

_____

512x512 pixels, Clip guided diffusion with initial image
